org.digijava.kernel.persistence

Class InMemoryCurrenciesManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.digijava.kernel.persistence.InMemoryCurrenciesManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InMemoryManager<AmpCurrency>

    public class InMemoryCurrenciesManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements InMemoryManager<AmpCurrency>
    Non-persistent implementation of InMemoryManager which is backed by an in-memory map.

    Mainly intended for testing purposes, where a full blown persistent system isn't required.

    Took from Haiti.
